I've heard people saying this was &quot;such an original story&quot;.  It wasn't
Other than that, I would have to say I enjoyed this movie from start to
finish.  Keanu Reeves is great, and the effects and camera direction were
very well done.  I would suggest this to any Sci-Fi fan, but I would also
add a recommendation for Ghost in the Shell.
